{
  "stem": "11290.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the reason was that even the best friends of my parents' families that were friends of-- my father had friends from his early youth, with which-- boys with whom he played.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were Gentile Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And some of them came to him and said you must understand, we can no longer associate with you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We have to regard our children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If we do, we would be seen as Jew friends or whatever they would call us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it would [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] affect the careers of our children. of our-- and that was the pressure that was exerted.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was partly-- it was mostly-- it was more pressure than authentic wish to do-- to do all these terrible things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I could not help-- I couldn't help overhearing it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I was then a young man in my parents' house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the radio was the big source of-- in those days was the big source.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no television, of course.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The radio was the big source of entertainment and information.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father, who was a patriotic German Jew, couldn't stand it that I even could leave the radio on to hear these speeches of Hitler and Goering and Goebbels.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I had to-- to do it low key in my room, so that my parents wouldn't be disturbed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was too much for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They thought it was a passing fancy, something that would pass over.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They didn't think it would take so many years to pass over and in such a horrible way.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
